      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAID IN FULL (1) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by a nose at this track in a handy 17.33 beating Doreen Keeping. Form from his last run is proving to be solid. Expected to be right there at the finish again. SON OF SPIKE (2) is a talented type and proved too classy last time to win by one length at this track in a handy 17.28 beating Evander Keeping. Has performed well from this box with a win and three minor placings to his name from eight starts. One of the key runners again. ALL IN KNOTS (6) was quickly into stride and found the front last start to record an all-the-way win (23.00) at this track in a Grade 5/6 over 400m. Was a winner at his only start from this draw. Form should stack up. SEND IT KYE (5) has won at this course and distance – sure to figure prominently.",
